<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Dashboard - Evil Capitalistic Corp</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>ğŸ“Š Dashboard</h1>
            <nav>
                <a href="/">ğŸ  Home</a>
                <a href="/dashboard">ğŸ“Š Dashboard</a>
                <a href="/admin">âš™ï¸ Admin</a>
                <a href="/logout">ğŸšª Logout</a>
            </nav>
        </header>
        
        <main style="padding: 3rem 2rem;">
            <h2>Welcome, <%= user.username %>!</h2>
            <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Role: <strong><%= user.role %></strong></p>
            
            <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-top: 2rem;">
                <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-left: 5px solid #1a1a2e;">
                    <h3 style="color: #1a1a2e; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Your Profile</h3>
                    <p style="color: #666; margin: 0.5rem 0;"><strong>Email:</strong> <%= user.email %></p>
                    <p style="color: #666; margin: 0.5rem 0;"><strong>Department:</strong> <%= user.department || 'N/A' %></p>
                    <p style="color: #666; margin: 0.5rem 0;"><strong>Salary:</strong> $<%= user.salary || 'N/A' %></p>
                    <a href="/user/<%= user.id %>" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; background: #ffd700; color: #1a1a2e; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; font-weight: 600;">View Full Profile â†’</a>
                </div>
                
                <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); border-left: 5px solid #ffd700;">
                    <h3 style="color: #1a1a2e; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Quick Actions</h3>
                    <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                        <li style="margin: 1rem 0;"><a href="/search" style="color: #1a1a2e; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">ğŸ“¦ Browse Products</a></li>
                        <li style="margin: 1rem 0;"><a href="/employees" style="color: #1a1a2e; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">ğŸ‘¥ Employee Directory</a></li>
                        <% if (user.role === 'admin' || user.role === 'superadmin') { %>
                            <li style="margin: 1rem 0;"><a href="/admin" style="color: #1a1a2e; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">âš™ï¸ Admin Panel</a></li>
                        <% } %>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <% if (user.notes) { %>
                <div style="background: #d4edda; border: 2px solid #28a745; padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
                    <p style="color: #155724; font-weight: 600;">ğŸ“ Notes:</p>
                    <p style="color: #155724;"><%= user.notes %></p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
            
            <div style="background: #fff3cd; border: 2px dashed #ffc107; padding: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
                <p style="color: #856404; font-weight: 600;">ğŸ’¡ Next Steps:</p>
                <p style="color: #856404;">Now that you're logged in, try accessing the admin panel. Can you escalate your privileges?</p>
                <p style="color: #856404; margin-top: 0.5rem;"><strong>Hint:</strong> Look at how the admin panel checks permissions...</p>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
